translation.Name: Hawaii Note - Unyielding 1
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: A T T E N T I O N   S U R V I V O R S !
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: We have established a safezone on the southeast coast near the memorial. We have food, water, shelter and warm beds.  Everyone is urged to join us and help humanity survive this outbreak.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_4: Together we will stand strong.. We are the united, We are the Unyielding!
